    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/5033751e692a05ec648d9d97f01648cf.poster.avif?t=1765133860\" width=170 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/5033751e692a05ec648d9d97f01648cf.webm?t=1765133860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/5033751e692a05ec648d9d97f01648cf.mp4?t=1765133860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >XxXxXxXxD[STORY]XxXxXxXxD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious objects suddenly and simultaneously appearing all over the world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown spaces and strange creatures spreading out there</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somewhere along the way, a special resource was said to be available from these creatures, called <strong>HEX</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whenever there is a whiff of money, there is always an underworld</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this dangerous city, a teenager named “Lea“Involved in the story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lust? or warfare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How you deal with <strong>HEX</strong> will have a big impact on the rest of your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/2c1f81c88dde42fd6abb83da29a49646.poster.avif?t=1765133860\" width=396 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/2c1f81c88dde42fd6abb83da29a49646.webm?t=1765133860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/2c1f81c88dde42fd6abb83da29a49646.mp4?t=1765133860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >XxXxXxXxD[BATTLE]XxXxXxXxD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you dive into a dungeon, fighting is inevitable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect more materials than you need and create items at the various mixing stations scattered throughout the area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some items work and some don't, depending on the monster you are facing, so keep repeating trial and error to conquer the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/eadc7e370a0be30b07797b34c17872ef.poster.avif?t=1765133860\" width=442 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/eadc7e370a0be30b07797b34c17872ef.webm?t=1765133860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187580/extras/eadc7e370a0be30b07797b34c17872ef.mp4?t=1765133860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >XxXxXxXxD[ACTIONS]XxXxXxXxD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have returned home safely from the dungeon, use the resources and money you have received,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the resources and money you receive to purchase materials and items, strengthen yourself, and prepare for the next stage of your exploration.</p>",
